                   There have been given for various (names) through the most admirable Phoibammon for his wife for the 1/3-share 
for the account of the public taxes of the annonae of the thirteenth indiction, one one-half one-third one-twelfth carat of gold,
 total 1 1/2 1/3 1/12 carat of gold. Aphous and Isak, diastoleis, through me, Iakybios, logographos, agree.
